dictionary.title: Broker
dictionary.description: The registered firm that buys and sells the stocks for others. All the stock transactions are made through registered brokers in Nepal.

dictionary.title: Floorsheet
dictionary.description: Where the exchange of shares take place. The floorsheet gives the idea of current or historical buyer broker, seller broker, rates, quantities and each transaction is assigned a unique contract number.

dictionary.title: Matching Amount
dictionary.description: Total amount of stock transaction of a broker with itself i.e., buying and selling a particular stock by the same broker.

dictionary.title: Stock Traded by Broker
dictionary.description: The details of the trades made by the broker.
